### Create a Booking for Special Needs Support
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "childId": 123,                       // ID of the registered child
  "parentId": 456,                      // ID of the parent making the booking
  "schoolId": 789,                      // ID of the school chosen
  "practitionerId": 321,                // ID of the healthcare practitioner (optional)
  "preferredDate": "2025-03-25",        // Preferred date for the booking
  "preferredTime": "14:00",             // Preferred time for the booking
  "purpose": "IEP Meeting",             // Purpose of the booking
  "notes": "Child requires wheelchair accessibility."
}


